# Salamander CTI detection ruleset  //  https://salacti.com
# From Fake Amazon Security Alert to HarborWatch Agent: ClickFix Delivery of a Custom Monitoring RAT  (defensive signatures; not endorsements)

alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"amazonalert.xyz"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100001; rev:1;)
alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"amazonattention.com"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100002; rev:1;)
alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"security.amazonassist.xyz"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100003; rev:1;)
